{
  "enabled": true,
  "name": "Validate Draw.io Edit",
  "description": "After any .drawio file is edited, validates the XML for common errors and fixes them automatically. Same validation as the fileCreated hook.",
  "version": "1",
  "when": {
    "type": "fileEdited",
    "patterns": [
      "**/*.drawio"
    ]
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "A .drawio file was just edited. Validate it for common errors:\n\n1. **Self-call 3-waypoint bug**: Search for edges with sourcePoint and targetPoint at same X (self-calls) that have 3 mxPoint elements inside Array. The 3rd point going back to lifeline is WRONG. Fix: remove 3rd waypoint, set targetPoint X = sourcePoint X, targetPoint Y = 2nd waypoint Y.\n\n2. **Self-closing edges**: Any `edge=\"1\"` cell ending with `/>` (no mxGeometry child). Fix: add child element.\n\n3. **mxfile wrapper**: File starts with `<mxfile>`. Fix: strip wrapper, keep bare `<mxGraphModel>`.\n\nIf ANY issue found: fix immediately, then re-export PNG.\nIf no issues: do nothing silently."
  }
}